# SUP switchover
redundancy force-switchover

# LC switchover
redundancy linecard-group switchover from slot <n>

# Show commands
show redundancy linecard all

# configuration
redundancy
  mode sso

  linecard-group 1 internal-switch
    class 1:n
    member slot 3 primary
    member slot 5 primary
    member slot 11 secondary
 
  linecard-group 2 internal-switch
    class 1:1
    member slot 10 primary
    member slot 12 secondary

